%include	/usr/lib/rpm/macros.perl
Summary:	FemFind - crawl your network resources
Summary(pl):	FemFind - przeszukiwanie zasobów sieciowych
Name:		FemFind
Version:	0.74
Release:	1
License:	GPL v2
Group:		Networking/Utilities
